Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个隐形穹顶罩住了切斯特磨坊镇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}an invisible dome crashed down on Chester's Mill,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.72,0:00:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使我们与世隔绝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}cutting us off from the rest of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.67,0:00:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么穹顶会在这里  以后还会有什么谜团\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why the dome is here or what mysteries lie ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.37,0:00:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们依然一无所知\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we still don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天它都考验我们的极限\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Every day it tests our limits,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.06,0:00:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,激发我们内心最善和最恶一面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}bringing out the best and the worst in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.41,0:00:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人说我们会永远困在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Some say we'll be stuck here forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们会一直奋力寻找出路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but we will never stop fighting to find a way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.56,0:00:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找山姆干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why are you looking for Sam?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.23,0:00:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得他一直认识梅兰妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think he's known who Melanie is all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.46,0:00:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在想你什么时候会出现呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was wondering when you'd show up.
