Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.78,0:00:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈妈说你有答案  我想知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My mother said you had answers; I want them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会再回去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm out for good now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.94,0:00:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些是手指印\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Those are the fingertips of a hand--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎安琪也留下了一点凶手的战利品\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Looks like Angie got a piece of whoever did this to her.
