Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.28,0:01:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.20,0:02:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要平安回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please come back.
