Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去找莱尔吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You going looking for Lyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.29,0:02:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  只要他还逍遥法外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah. Well, as long as he's out there on the loose,
