Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我断后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm just gonna hang back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确保我们不会被别人偷袭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know, make sure no one else sneaks up on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈妈的日记\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My mom's journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小詹姆斯  停下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Junior, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小詹姆斯  当心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Junior, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.46,0:08:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芭比  小心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Barbie! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.03,0:08:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}穹顶之下  第二季第六集
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山姆  你没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sam, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被砸了  但没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh! Bashed up, but all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小詹姆斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Junior!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小詹姆斯  你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Junior, you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留在那里  我去找人帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stay there! I'll get some help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}God...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.47,0:08:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的头在流血\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your head's bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本可能会更糟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It could've been worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.75,0:08:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你推了我一把\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thanks for the push.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这是莱尔干的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think Lyle did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:09:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小镇理发师会做炸药吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The town barber makes bombs?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一直诡计多端\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's always been a crafty guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且自从穹顶落下以后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And he's gone crazier than a rat in a jar
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.36,0:09:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他比笼中困鼠还疯狂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}since the dome came down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.84,0:09:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很聪明  会用日记作为陷阱诱饵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's smart enough to bait the trap with the journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能原路返回了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, we're not getting out the way we came.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们要走那条路了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Guess we'll try that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}After you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.18,0:09:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just-just stay still, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.04,0:09:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得跟那个酒鬼一起下去是个好主意吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You thought it was a good idea to go down there with that drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他为我做的事比你做的还多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's done more for me than you ever did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来干什么  又没人叫你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are you even doing here? Nobody called you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去哪里你管不着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't need your permission to go here or anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.69,0:09:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉姆  消停消停好吗  我在给你儿子包扎呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim, give it a rest, okay? I'm trying to bandage your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.55,0:09:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听到你通过对讲机找芭比了  他人呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I heard you radio Barbie. Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和山姆在追踪莱尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sam and I were tracking down Lyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.66,0:09:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芭比来找我们  然后突然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Barbie came after us, and then all of a sudden,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被什么绊了一下  下面就塌了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I tripped on something and then there was a cave-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.06,0:09:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们进这个储物柜里面了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You went through this locker?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们人呢  他们没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where are they? Are they all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面有很多石头和杂物把路堵住了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's a bunch of rocks and stuff blocking them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得把他们救出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have to get them out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没注意吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In case you have noticed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.70,0:10:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还有更严重的问题要处理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we've got bigger problems than those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.56,0:10:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是红雨中的酸性物质破坏了表层土壤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The acidity in the red rain must have fried the topsoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这玩意儿被吹的到处都是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, well, it's blowing around everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.17,0:10:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把什么都覆盖住了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and coating everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括穹顶里面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}including the inside of the dome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.94,0:10:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穹顶是半透明的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Which is semi-permeable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果穹顶壁被遮挡住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If the dome walls get clogged,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空气就进不来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}no air's gonna be able to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们都会窒息而亡  所有人都会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And then we suffocate. All of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:31.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还有多长时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How long until that happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也可以采取措施的  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are steps we can take, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.16,0:10:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水雾扩散\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mist dispersal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽快把水撒到空中让尘土落地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get water into the air as quickly as possible to ground the dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用消防水管  风扇  或者是大型风车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fire hose, fan, uh, a giant windmill, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前让孩子们制作过一些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I had the kids working on some,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我得把这事放了一放\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but I had to put it on the back burner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们还有一切制作材料\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We still have all the materials, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少你的主意比茱莉亚的有用多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At least your idea is doing more than Julia's to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是想眼睁睁看着芭比和山姆死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You just want to see Barbie and Sam dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.85,0:10:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一切都取决于我了是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, I guess it's up to me, then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们可能在老水泥厂里面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know, they could be in part of the old cement factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去找隧道的地图\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We find a map of the tunnel system,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能会找到其它入口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we might find another way in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能找到地图吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you find one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱尔可能已经出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lyle might have already gotten out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本无从得知他是不是还在里面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's no way of knowing if he's down there anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在外面总比在里面对付芭比和山姆强\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Better he's out here than hunting Barbie and Sam down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他要是在外面  也同样危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, but if he's back up here, he's just as dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟山姆发现莱尔的目标不止是安琪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sam and I found out that Lyle wasn't just after Angie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.72,0:11:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想杀四只手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's after the four hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他怎么知道四只手的事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How does he know about the hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前我妈妈画了一幅我们托着穹顶的画\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My mom drew a picture of us holding up the dome way back when.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱尔以为要是我们死了  被提就会到来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, Lyle thinks that if we're dead, the Rapture comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说他也想杀你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, he wanted to kill you, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  他知道我会追踪他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah. He knew I'd follow him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.03,0:11:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确定隧道里面的炸弹目标是我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm pretty sure that bomb down there was meant for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得确保乔和诺莉的安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need to make sure Joe and Norrie are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-小心点  -我跟他一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Be careful. - I'll go with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅兰妮  我不...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Melanie, I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们也是我的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're my friends, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会保护她的  我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll make sure she's safe, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从小就认识莱尔对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, you known Lyle all your life, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.51,0:11:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  我们从小一起长大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, we were friends growing up.
