Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要追杀四只手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and he's coming after the four hands.
