Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-小詹姆斯告诉我的  -不  他没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Junior told me. - No, he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你二十五年前就认识她了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You knew her 25 years ago.
