Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救起的时候你就知道她是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}since Julia rescued her from the lake,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是你什么都没有说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}only you didn't say a word to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么不说  山姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why didn't you say anything, Sam?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.88,0:17:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说梅兰妮起死回生了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}About Melanie being back from the dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你告诉我我该怎么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You tell me how to start that conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  你能不能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right, you know what? Would you just
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先回答你一直在回避的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}answer the question that you keep dodging?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.20,0:17:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说谢谢吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You gonna say thank you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是莱尔的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That Lyle's?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Has to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.85,0:18:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得他是从这里出去的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You think he went out this way?
