Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢天谢地  你个蠢蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, thank God! You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们担心死你了  到处找你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We were worried about you. We looked all over.
