Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.07,0:19:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是莱尔想杀了我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not with Lyle wanting to kill us.
