Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.21,0:19:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才杀了安琪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's why he killed Angie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为这个吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's the reason?
