Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许我们也只有这样才能出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe that's the only way any of us are gonna get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It didn't work for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.80,0:19:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我死了  又回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I died. I came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:52.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Will she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:55.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我过了一段时间才回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It took awhile for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.74,0:20:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得穹顶选择我们大家是有原因的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think the dome choose all of us for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在要勇敢面对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And now we have to deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.91,0:20:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,齐心协力想办法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need to figure it out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.23,0:20:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  梅兰妮  我觉得我们不能妄动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry, Melanie. I think we need to stay put.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安琪会想让我保证你们安全的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Angie would want me to keep you all safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.41,0:20:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安琪会想要答案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Angie would've wanted answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.64,0:20:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非得到答案  否则她不会罢休\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She wouldn't have stopped till she got them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.99,0:20:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小詹姆斯  我们必须这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Junior, we have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我情愿冒险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I would rather risk
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再死一次  也不愿继续蒙在鼓里了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}dying again than not knowing why I'm here any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道该从哪开始吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you have any idea where to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个湖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.09,0:20:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那里开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We start there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.89,0:20:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得莱尔跳下去了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You think Lyle jumped?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正不是爬下去的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, he sure as hell didn't climb down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许他又回去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, you know what? Maybe he went right back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了另一条路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Got out that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了  我向右走的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I told you, I went right--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是回了你那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it brought me back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没听见它碰到了东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't hear it hit anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西肯定深不见底\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This thing must be deep as hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.57,0:21:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Something's off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是保守的说法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Understatement.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.19,0:21:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考虑到我们刚走了那么远\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I mean, given how far we just walked,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该已经到穹顶边上了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we should've hit the dome wall by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许穹顶没降下那么深\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe the dome doesn't come down this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我们掌握的一切都表明它有这么深\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Except that everything we know about it says that it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.98,0:21:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定你刚才是向右走的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're sure you went right back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.94,0:21:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你猜怎么着  伙计\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, you know what, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.43,0:21:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受够你说我骗人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sick of you calling me a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有谁知道你的底细\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who the hell knows your story anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.27,0:21:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和穹顶同一天出现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You show up the day the dome does.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人知道你从哪来  你也不说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No one knows where you came from and you don't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.70,0:21:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不该你告诉我怎么回事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, shouldn't you be telling me what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.92,0:21:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是从1988年就知道蛋的事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}'Cause you've known about the egg since 1988
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和梅兰妮  莱尔  波琳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when you and Melanie, Lyle, Pauline,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起发现的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when you all found it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.31,0:21:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还有所隐瞒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know more than you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, that makes two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.05,0:21:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到水泥厂的地图了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you find the cement factory maps?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.61,0:21:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我直接拿了一切  然后带过来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just grabbed everything and brought them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.97,0:21:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面的土跟外面差不多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is almost as bad as outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.52,0:21:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话  茱莉亚  这沙尘暴我在行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Honestly, Julia, the storm is more my area.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:21:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  是科学你都在行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, yes, all science is your area.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.81,0:22:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是切斯特磨坊镇的老师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm a teacher in Chester's Mill.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.98,0:22:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是洛克希德的工程师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not an engineer for Lockheed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道自己有多大本事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am all too aware of my limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.29,0:22:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道你能闯多大祸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I know what kind of damage you're capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.69,0:22:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不相信我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.92,0:22:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原谅你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I forgave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.22,0:22:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是一回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's not the same thing.
