Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.23,0:27:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在努力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, I'm trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.45,0:27:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在高中都教些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are you doing teaching high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.56,0:27:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想问我是怎么搞砸自己的人生的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You mean how'd I screw up my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.25,0:27:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是这个意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.10,0:27:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我来切斯特磨坊镇前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was headed to Cornell
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.13,0:28:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本打算去康奈尔大学念书\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}before I came to Chester's Mill.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.62,0:28:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么改变主意了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why the change?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.78,0:28:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸爸病了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My dad got sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.19,0:28:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他去世之前我得照顾他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I had to take care of him before he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.32,0:28:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的故事估计跟我也差不多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can't be all that different from your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.04,0:28:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你原来是名记者  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You were a journalist, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.77,0:28:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来切斯特磨坊镇是你梦想中的工作吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Was Chester's Mill your dream job?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.87,0:28:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不  不是  -我说吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- No, it wasn't. - See?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.60,0:28:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们两个都不想来这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Neither of us wanted to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.69,0:28:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们现在却在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.75,0:28:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是命运\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.48,0:28:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们做了选择  然后来到了这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We made choices and we ended up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.41,0:28:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我没照顾我爸爸的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe I could've helped a lot more people
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.10,0:28:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我能帮助更多的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if I hadn't helped my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.18,0:28:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但往事不可逆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But that wasn't gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.04,0:28:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们就得做这事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, you and me are stuck doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.96,0:28:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要和吉姆合作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why'd you work with Jim?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.90,0:28:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我觉得他的心眼还是很好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because I thought his heart was in the right place.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.58,0:28:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我搞错了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was wrong about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.33,0:28:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我没看错你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't think I'm wrong about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.63,0:28:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.93,0:29:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灰尘消散了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The dust cleared out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.82,0:29:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  现在该怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah. So, what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.00,0:29:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经过去了几个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's been hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.07,0:29:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那颗蛋知道我们在这\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The egg knows we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.73,0:29:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能感受到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.88,0:29:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它好像是在等着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's like it's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.31,0:29:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道这颗蛋不肯现身\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All I know, this egg isn't showing itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.40,0:29:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我们都在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Even with all of us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.85,0:29:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我们要一起做一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe we have to do something together.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.84,0:29:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.55,0:29:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如安琪还在的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like when Angie was here,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.44,0:29:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起触碰了迷你穹顶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and we all touched the mini-dome?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.23,0:29:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅兰妮是最初的四只手之一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Melanie was one of the original four hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.93,0:29:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许她还算数\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe she still counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.05,0:29:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以安琪是可以取代的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So Angie's replaceable?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.23,0:29:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人要取代你姐姐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No one's replacing your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.92,0:29:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但诺莉说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But Norrie's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.00,0:29:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正也没别的主意了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't hear any other ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.95,0:29:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起作用了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's working!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.18,0:30:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么现在梅兰妮回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, why's Melanie back now?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.32,0:30:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吓唬我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To haunt me?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.32,0:30:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带给大家更多痛苦吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To bring everyone more pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.73,0:30:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穹顶之下不都是痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not all pain under this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.44,0:30:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The hell it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.70,0:30:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天就是新的噩梦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Every day is a new nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.22,0:30:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穹顶是一种缓慢的死刑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dome's a slow execution for everyone in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.36,0:30:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最应该清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You of all people should know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.29,0:30:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  但我会面对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, but I deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.23,0:30:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你寻找让...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You look for what makes...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.18,0:30:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让继续生活下去值得的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}what makes going on worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.49,0:30:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如说茱莉亚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Take Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.49,0:30:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟她在一起...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Being with her, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.88,0:30:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是让我改邪归正的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it's a chance for me to be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.92,0:30:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穹顶也让我害怕  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The dome scares me, too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.32,0:30:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不全是痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...it's not all pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.49,0:30:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候我会看见梅兰妮的脸出现在黑暗中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sometimes I see Melanie's face in the dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.99,0:30:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始流血不止\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with the blood starting to pour out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.31,0:31:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我能改变生命中的一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I could change one thing in my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.89,0:31:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是那件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that'd be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.85,0:31:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你的感受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, I know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.71,0:31:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.74,0:31:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你杀了谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who'd you kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.36,0:31:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.59,0:31:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鉴于目前的形势\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Given the way things are going...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.66,0:31:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我会再次杀人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...I know it's gonna happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.01,0:31:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想那样做  但是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I mean, I don't want that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.29,0:31:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候你看见他们的脸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sometimes you see their faces...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.45,0:31:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你开始想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...you wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.18,0:31:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会在另一边等你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are they gonna be waiting for you on the other side?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.21,0:31:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.36,0:31:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.15,0:31:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天  我发现她在这边等我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The other day, I found her waiting for me on this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.84,0:31:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能对她说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What the hell can I say to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.84,0:32:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们离开这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We get out of here,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.61,0:32:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你可以试试\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}maybe you can give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.78,0:32:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道梅兰妮最想知道答案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know Melanie just wants answers more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.49,0:32:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至于25年前你们之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As far as what happened between you two
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.91,0:32:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生的事  那是你们的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}25 years ago, you know, that's between you and her.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.69,0:32:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.37,0:32:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你没让我摔下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thanks for not letting me fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.04,0:32:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是岩石造成的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, those aren't from rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.30,0:32:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些抓伤是怎么来的  山姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where'd you get those scratches, Sam?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.44,0:32:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个放在那边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Put that there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.91,0:32:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个刚好能放进这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And this one will fit right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.33,0:32:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来连接导火线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I connect the fuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.79,0:32:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢道路维修部门\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank God for the department of roads and repair.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.18,0:32:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在祈祷吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You praying?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.25,0:33:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  但我很希望这能管用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. But I hope to God this works.
